info.name: Zaikedaar Paneer Biryani + Murgh Keema Combo (Serves 1-2)
info.description: (1 Biryani served with raita & gulab jamun + 1 Gravy + 3 Tawa Paratha) Begin a wholesome daawat with soft, diced paneer marinated in 23 shahi masalas, dum-pukht with golden basmati. Save more as you relish our much-loved juicy, minced chicken kheema and soft, fluffy kulchas.

info.name: Lazeez Bhuna Murgh Biryani + Murgh Keema Combo (Serves 1-2)
info.description: (1 Biryani served with raita & gulab jamun + 1 Gravy + 2 Kulcha) Start your royal jashn with raseele chicken pieces marinated in exuberant bhuna spices, dum-pukht with long-grain basmati rice. Add juicy, minced chicken kheema and soft, fluffy kulchas to complete your daawat.

info.name: Lazeez Bhuna Murgh Biryani + Murgh Makhani Combo (Serves 1-2)
info.description: (1 Biryani served with raita & gulab jamun + 1 Gravy + 3 Tawa Paratha ) Set up a daawat like never before with our culinary jewel of raseele chicken pieces, marinated in exuberant bhuna masalas and dum-pukht with aromatic rice. Save more as you relish it with the Mughlai juicy, grilled chicken in a creamy yet spicy gravy and crispy, tawa parathas!

info.name: Murgh Afghani Tikka + Murgh Makhani Combo (Serves 1-2)
info.description: (1 Biryani served with raita & gulab jamun + 1 Gravy + 3 Tawa Paratha) Get together for a yaadgaar daawat with this rich & creamy biryani, made with tender chicken marinated in fresh dahi & masalas. Save more with the combo of Old Delhi's all-time classic of juicy grilled chicken prepared in a creamy yet masaledaar gravy and crispy tawa parathas!

info.name: Dum Gosht Biryani + Murgh Makhani Combo (Serves 1-2)
info.description: (1 Biryani served with raita & gulab jamun + 1 Gravy + 3 Tawa Paratha) Relish this ruhani daawat of raseela gosht marinated in 23 royal masalas & dum-pukht to perfection. Let your guests savour it with juicy, minced chicken kheema and desi tawa parathas!

info.name: Raan-e-Murgh Biryani + Murgh Makhani Combo (Serves 1-2)
info.description:
(1 Biryani served with raita & gulab jamun + 1 Gravy + 3 Tawa Paratha)
Indulge in a majestic daawat of premium whole leg chicken thigh, marinated in 23 royal masalas & laid atop long-grain basmati rice. Pair this classic with Old Delhi's shahi juicy grilled chicken prepared in a creamy yet masaledaar gravy. Complete your feast with crispy, flaky parathas!

info.name: Special Combo-Murgh Biryani+2 Gravies,Breads & Beverage (Serves 4)
info.description: (1 Biryani served with raita & gulab jamun + 2 Gravies + 3 Tawa Parathas + 2 Kulchas + 1 Coca-Cola) Get extra savings of Rs 110 with an extraordinary murgh daawat, Savor our flavorful Lazeez Bhuna Murgh biryani and pair it with our royal chicken gravies, full of rich, flavorful masalas. Sum up the feast with parathas, kulchas and Coca-Cola!
